{"word":"προσελαύνω","slug":"προσελαύνω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>προσελαύνω</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>-ελάσω</el>) (attic <el>-ελῶ</el>) (aor1 <el>-ήλᾰσα</el>) </el><p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to drive</i> or <i>chase to</i> a place, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>:—<a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> <i>to be driven</i> or <i>fixed to</i>, <el>πρός τι</el> <b><a href='S:Plutarch'>Plut.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b>seemingly <a href='S:intransitive'>intr.</a>,<p/></div><div class='li750'><b>1. </b>(<a href='S:subaudi, subaudito'>sub.</a> <el>ἵππον</el>), <i>to ride towards, ride up</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b>; <el>οἱ προσελαύνοντες</el> <i>the cavalry</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b>(<a href='S:subaudi, subaudito'>sub.</a> <el>στρατόν</el>), <i>to march up, arrive</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}